ğŸ’¡ Hint: Look at the first line of the request (GET /index.html HTTP/1.1) and extract the filename.

âœ… Checkpoint: If you visit localhost:8080/about.html, it should serve about.html from disk.
ğŸ“Œ Step 6: Handle Multiple Clients

ğŸ‘‰ Goal: Make your server handle more than one client at a time.
